%section#plan
  %h1
    %span Plan/Price
  .container
    .row.text-center
      .col-lg-4
        .panel.panel-danger
          .panel-heading
            %small= t('.plan_1_text')
          %ul.list-group
            %li.list-group-item
              = image_tag('about/price_1.png')
              %h2.text-danger FREE
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_price')
              %strong= t('.free')
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_storage')
              %strong
                10
                %small (※)
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_size')
              %strong= "32#{t('.plan_player_count')}"
            %li.list-group-item
              =link_to root_path, class: 'btn btn-danger' do
                = t('.plan_1_action')
      .col-lg-4
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            %small= t('.plan_2_text')
          %ul.list-group
            %li.list-group-item
              = image_tag('about/price_2.png')
              %h2 BASIC
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_price')
              %strong 500円
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_storage')
              %strong ∞（無制限）
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_size')
              %strong 128名
            %li.list-group-item
              =link_to @shop_url, target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-primary' do
                = t('.plan_2_action')
              %br
              %small ※外部の購入ページに遷移します
      .col-lg-4
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            %small= t('.plan_3_text')
          %ul.list-group
            %li.list-group-item
              = image_tag('about/price_3.png')
              %h2 PREMIUM
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_price')
              %strong --
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_storage')
              %strong --
            %li.list-group-item
              %small= t('.plan_size')
              %strong --
            %li.list-group-item
              =link_to '#', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-primary' do
                = t('.plan_3_action')
    %div.mb-30.text-center
      %p
        ※無料で作成可能なトーナメント数を増やすオプションもあります。
        %br
        詳しくは「
        %a(href="/gift")
          無料のトーナメント作成数を増やす
        」のページをご確認ください。
    %div.text-center

